ow about a greengrocer's shop?<br>Or maybe you've always wanted to sell your own creation? The choice is yours! Level up your shop through all the phases of popularity. From an unknown local shop to a regional star! Marine décor will make it easier to sell fish, country décor will help you sell fruits and vegetables, and fancy décor should be your choice when selling sculptures and paintings!.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1319400/extras/27a5997bd7f44ef0ae22fcc9faac2688.poster.avif?t=1723728292\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1319400/extras/27a5997bd7f44ef0ae22fcc9faac2688.webm?t=1723728292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1319400/extras/27a5997bd7f44ef0ae22fcc9faac2688.mp4?t=1723728292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Meet new friends!</strong><br>The city bustles with life. It is worth getting to know its characters and their stories. And who knows, maybe you will get to be really close to someone.",
